Build a cross-compiler from source.
Steps taken from:

https://istarc.wordpress.com/2014/07/21/stm32f4-build-your-toolchain-from-scratch/


More or less, run the shell scripts in this order:

01_mkdir.sh
02_download.sh
03_extract.sh
04_build_binutils.sh
05_build_gcc.sh
06_build_newlib.sh
07_build_gcc_again.sh
